"Ask your system administrator to remove <code>proc_open()</code> from "
"the <a href=\":url\">disable_functions</a> setting in "
"<code>php.ini</code>."
msgstr ""
"Be systemadministratoren din om å fjerne <code>proc_open()</code> fra "
"innstillingen <a href=\":url\">disable_functions</a> i "
